<br>Lease Term: 12 Months
<br>Tenants responsible for all utilities
<br>No smoking and no pets (no exceptions), please.
<br>
<br>*$49 non-refundable application fee per each applicant age 18 and older.
<br>
<br>Key Words: Seattle, Mt Baker, North Beacon Hill, Rainier Vista, I-5, I-90, Lakeshore.
  </blockquote>

  <b>Amenities</b>
